{"tid":347853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撐港人拒自稱中國人　北師大教授因言入罪遭提前解僱","createTime":"2017-08-05T07:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T11:34:29.000Z","uid":48083,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0953a5e7474817816c9430f187bd6bd11046f523","tid":347853,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:43:05.000Z","msg":"北京師範大學古籍與傳統文化研究院副教授史杰鵬，被校方指其網上言論「與主流價值觀不一致」、「逾越意識形態管理紅綫，違反政治紀律」，故提前3年解聘。史杰鵬過去在微博曾以帳號「梁惠王」多次發表備受爭議的言論，質疑中央當局的言行，例如批評中共已故領導人毛澤東為「魔頭」、「最應該炸死的就是他」，又曾支持香港本土派指「認為自己是香港人而非中國人有什麼錯」。<br />\n<br />\n現年46歲的史杰鵬在北京師範大學已任職近20年，主要研究古文字學、訓詁學和先秦兩漢文獻學等，同時以筆名「梁惠王」出版《亭長小武》、《赤壁》等歷史小說。不過，他針對中共管治的言論不時會被左報批評為「師者敗類」，，例如他先後於2014年和2015年的《南方都市報》發表〈為什麼當兵的都是窮人〉和〈軍人只是一種職業〉的評論文章，而被解放軍撰文斥責他「污損」軍人。<br />\n<br />\n另外，史杰鵬在2012年評論港人的身份認同時更稱「認為自己是香港人而非中國人有什麼錯，我就認為我是南昌人」。對於愛國教育，他表示「什麼愛國教育，什麼國民教育，都是扯淡。作為一個公民活著，就足夠了，不需要作為一個愛國者活著」，更明指中國的政治課是「洗腦政治課」。<br />\n<br />\n（圖片來源：梁惠王微博截圖、新浪網截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/224662/%e6%9b%be%e6%92%90%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e6%8b%92%e8%87%aa%e7%a8%b1%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e4%ba%ba%e3%80%80%e5%8c%97%e5%b8%ab%e5%a4%a7%e6%95%99%e6%8e%88%e5%9b%a0%e8%a8%80%e5%85%a5%e7%bd%aa%e9%81%ad%e6%8f%90/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F224662%2F%25e6%259b%25be%25e6%2592%2590%25e6%25b8%25af%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%258b%2592%25e8%2587%25aa%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e3%2580%2580%25e5%258c%2597%25e5%25b8%25ab%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e6%2595%2599%25e6%258e%2588%25e5%259b%25a0%25e8%25a8%2580%25e5%2585%25a5%25e7%25bd%25aa%25e9%2581%25ad%25e6%258f%2590%2F&d=RteHjx9wNTTgmW3pMpHAcywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=93f50a22\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/224662/%e6%9b%be%e6%92%90%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e6%8b%92%e8%87%aa%e7%a8%b1%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e4%ba%ba%e3%80%80%e5%8c%97%e5%b8%ab%e5%a4%a7%e6%95%99%e6%8e%88%e5%9b%a0%e8%a8%80%e5%85%a5%e7%bd%aa%e9%81%ad%e6%8f%90/</a>"},{"pid":"99d40a063b48586c874e8b1ff065a8e4fd23d941","tid":347853,"uid":82103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258b41225839f9ac7b757c3084492f6074208831","tid":347853,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6932906d1cca8ae1384ec438d29b29a73d503773","tid":347853,"uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:00:15.000Z","msg":"死剩種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c35517e5858b1e503e500ea40a08d926514dbc7","tid":347853,"uid":86277,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:11:35.000Z","msg":"講吓人話啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c397661052fe1c85f91dd478f86bfc59ec2d69","tid":347853,"uid":31559,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:17:33.000Z","msg":"係中國作為一個有知識既人活著係一種痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6d629cb651f52b5252ea3f8ce50351683b3d74","tid":347853,"uid":55568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:17:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講吓人話啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係佢見鬼講人話<br />\n呢d人最早死"},{"pid":"63f584e0f02c50c8c29718cdbf8be0915b73e9c2","tid":347853,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8bb3047e4d6ae2ee649b8bc1c04c5bf8f6af37c","tid":347853,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:27:14.000Z","msg":"已經冇哂感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da0498705fef1423b8087355acc2c8b4fac609b","tid":347853,"uid":41658,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:04:15.000